episodes.title: From a Religious Cult to Filmmaking w/ Giovannie Espiritu | Film Goals Podcast Ep. 43
episodes.description: #filmmaker #podcasts #documentary Giovannie Espiritu is an actress, writer, producer and director. She talks about her past in a cult and how she got her start in the film industry. She is a Telly Award winner, and acting coach. We talk about her award winning projects and more. Follow Giovannie: https://www.instagram.com/giospirit2/ https://giovannieespiritu.com/ Follow Film Goals: https://www.instagram.com/angel_filmgoals/ https://www.filmgoals.com/
